How to install iOS 7 Beta without UDID / Developers account:


1) iTunes and connect your (iPad, iPhone, iPod touch 5) with your PC via USB cable.

2) Hold down the Option key in OS X (Windows use Shift key) and click on "Update" not on "Restore".

3) Select the iOS 7 beta file you downloaded, updating the device to iOS 7 beta. 

Done.
